{"tid":2010340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警甴：搜出汽油彈原材料—電油 毛巾 打火機","createTime":"2020-05-10T10:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T03:31:25.000Z","uid":216992,"like":12,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7ed3c230a7365d0e7df73b6864a10c08162d33","tid":2010340,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"【警方於旺角新世紀廣場示威者身上搜出疑似汽油彈原材料】<br />\n<br />\n今日下午，有示威者先後於港九新界多個商場内聚集，部分人手持橫額、高叫口號、破壞社會安寧。其間警方收到市民報案，因此進入多個商場執法。<br />\n<br />\n於傍晚5時許，警方在旺角新世紀廣場三樓位置截停多名示威者，其中一人身上藏有懷疑製造汽油彈原料， 包括電油、<span style=\"color: red;\">多條毛巾及數個打火機</span>。警方不排除有人企圖在示威活動中使用該批物品，嚴重危害在場人士安全。警方拘捕一人並已撿走相關物品，會繼續調查案件。"},{"pid":"258adb6e5d9c5720d0101cfe6f7ae90c22b383a3","tid":2010340,"uid":216992,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLAweLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLAweLJ.jpg&h=632afaba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57b27b4cac0165b30ee152c6f38d12041dd6e9d7","tid":2010340,"uid":216992,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死"},{"pid":"1f82413edc7bc6d4aa5240da1c765ed124a3f7be","tid":2010340,"uid":224657,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"波都係用嚟襲警架啦，有乜咁出奇"},{"pid":"c663571921cd3f1919eea2ca08ef2a0d46a054af","tid":2010340,"uid":216992,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"唱歌、手持橫額、高叫口號=破壞社會安寧=可以開槍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmo